2024 Insurance Release Notes

See these release notes for the Insurance releases in 2024.

Insurance Summer â€˜24 Release Notes: Discover how to provide quick access to policy and claim details with the Financial Services Client Portal, use Einstein Copilot for Insurance to save time on record summaries, and view customer interactions with marketing emails using the Engagement Timeline.

Insurance Spring '24 Release Notes: Use flows to verify callers and producers, rate large group quotes, enroll census members in plans, delete census members in bulk, enable customers to self-enroll, and identify correct pricing procedures throughout the policy lifecycle. Help agents navigate claim records with the Insurance Agent Console.

Insurance Winter '24 Release Notes: Simplify large group quoting and enrollment workflows with new Lightning web components, leverage flexibility to enroll new hires or terminate policies during the contract term, calculate and view employee and employer contributions during bulk and new hire enrollment, and create relationship graphs for Insurance customers using templates.
